description: Gets a list of changelogs from Audit Manager.

parameters.name: assessmentId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the assessment.

nested_items.name: changeLogs
nested_items.description: The list of user activity for the control.

nested_items.name: objectType
nested_items.description: The object that was changed, such as an assessment, control, or control set.

nested_items.name: objectName
nested_items.description: The name of the object that changed. This could be the name of an assessment, control, or control set.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time when the action was performed and the changelog record was created.

nested_items.name: createdBy
nested_items.description: The user or role that performed the action.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token that's used to fetch the next set of results.
